[normal]AFS0026[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written [bold]evidence submitted by[bold] Future[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Our response focuses on
[normal] 
[normal]- 
[normal]The functions and responsibilities in relation to academies and free schools of local authorities and other 
[normal]organisations operating between the Secretary of State and individual schools; what these functions and responsibilities should be; and what gaps there are in support for schools at this level
